=head2 B<REQUIRED> MetadataTableConfigurationResult => L<Paws::S3::MetadataTableConfigurationResult>

The metadata table configuration for a general purpose bucket.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Status => Str

The status of the metadata table. The status values are:

=over

=item *

C<CREATING> - The metadata table is in the process of being created in
the specified table bucket.

=item *

C<ACTIVE> - The metadata table has been created successfully and
records are being delivered to the table.

=item *

C<FAILED> - Amazon S3 is unable to create the metadata table, or Amazon
S3 is unable to deliver records. See C<ErrorDetails> for details.

